Hey Sandy,

Please post a PDF of the doc or some text format so we can track changes in this jira. Eg upload a new doc with each rev.

Wrt your definition of dominant share, we want to implement weighted DRF here, and per section 4.3 in the paper:

{noformat}The deﬁnition of a dominant share for user i changes to
s_i = max_j{ u_i,j / w_i,j }
where u_i,j is user i’s share of resource j{noformat}

Neatly done, Sandy. I have one comment: given we have ResourceType now, it might be better to get rid of memory/cpu specific methods in ResourceWeights. The following two methods should suffice.

{code}
float getWeight(ResourceType rt);
void setWeight(ResourceType rt, float weight);
{code}

